The purpose of Unit 35 Merox is to extract RSH (mercaptan sulfur) from straight run LPG from the Crude Unit debutanizers and from olefins from the two FCC gas plant debutanizers. It is also possible to treat straight run gasoline from Crude Unit debutanizers and light cat naphtha from the Cat Gas Splitter.

