The purpose of Unit 38 Szorb is to remove sulfur from the combined stream of #1 & #2 FCC Debutanizer bottoms (Raw Cat Naphtha). The FCC feed can be supplemented from tankage. It is also possible to run the Szorb unit when the FCC is down if there is sufficient inventory in tankage.
